<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi folks,</p>

<p>The following code won't work:</p>

<p>$acl-&gt;addResource('funcA','classA');
$acl-&gt;addResource('funcA','classB');</p>

<p>It didn't do it in ZF1 and also doesn't appear to do it in ZF2. We recently came across it in a project.</p>

<p>It would be great if this could be namespace related or named. The obvious work around is:</p>

<p>$acl-&gt;addResource('classA_funcA','classA');
$acl-&gt;addResource('classB_funcA','classB');</p>

<p>Thanks</p>

<p>Antony</p>

